{"tid":874705,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★港大民調顯示，四分一受訪者每月儲超過1萬港元。家庭主婦每月儲蓄4,300元","createTime":"2018-10-24T11:38:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-25T05:47:29.000Z","uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"a3ca8ef4fde3751471b867103a71994b175af39b","tid":874705,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T11:38:36.000Z","msg":"香港大學民研計劃發布最新民調顯示，香港家庭主婦儲蓄習慣有待改善。<br />\n<br />\n該調查發現，現時七成受訪香港人有儲蓄習慣，但只有約半數受訪家庭主婦有此習慣。<br />\n<br />\n港人普遍每月平均儲蓄7,000港元，其中30至49歲香港人及男性的儲蓄最多，分別為每月8,537元和7,760元，逾四分一受訪者每月儲蓄更超過1萬港元。而家庭主婦則每月儲蓄4,300元，比儲蓄最多的組別低超過一半。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20181024/bkn-20181024165549334-1024_00842_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20181024%2Fbkn-20181024165549334-1024_00842_001.html&d=TfZYDYXcrxxb4%2B8FkDEgtsKJ7zzy8RXHrd%2FDXtMH0Y8%3D&h=caf7bce2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20181024/bkn-20181024165549334-1024_00842_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"8d515418d9843bddc8bcc859488e58742c34993f","tid":874705,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T11:39:40.000Z","msg":"貧窮問題已徹底解決<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8f7589e1f8eeb53bb8245e23fc181218be3ed4d","tid":874705,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T11:40:39.000Z","msg":"不用興建公屋了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c832463a8778631159af91f65652c96ec52fa2d8","tid":874705,"uid":46170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T11:41:08.000Z","msg":"唔儲點北上去大灣區旅行報答蛆國啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46ee8ed24fe3c51508b8e26f188108275a3e86f4","tid":874705,"uid":163324,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T11:44:57.00